item.title: Tech NEWS 2021-08-10
item.description: Netflix is working on a bunch of new reality shows, and you’re invited (2 minute read) Netflix has opened up casting for future programming to anyone over the age of 18 in the US, Canada, United Kingdom, and Ireland.

item.title: Tech NEWS 2021-07-15
item.description: Amazon bought Facebook’s satellite team to help build its Starlink competitor (3 minute read) Amazon has purchased Facebook’s small-satellite division.

item.title: Tech NEWS 2021-05-11
item.description: Google foils Roku’s YouTube TV ban, adds service to the main YouTube app (3 minute read) Roku recently removed the YouTube TV app from its store due to a disagreement with its contract with Google.

item.title: Tech NEWS 2020-08-12
item.description: Airbnb plans to confidentially file for IPO this month (1 minute read) Airbnb is planning to submit a confidential filing with the SEC to go public this month, with shares trading by the end of the year.
